data.text:
Outlook

A relentless rebounder who has the potential to develop into a solid all-around performer...Possesses a great work ethic.

High School - Champlin Park H.S.

A 2008 graduate of Champlin Park High School...Averaged 12.2 points and 11.4 rebounds per game as senior to go along with 56.2 field-goal percentage...Helped team to 15-12 win-loss mark and was named team’s Most Valuable Player as well as Defensive Player of Year...Also tabbed team’s Defensive Player of Year as junior in addition to being honorable-mention all-conference selection.

Personal

Full name: Chukwuemeka Chikwelu Okafor...Age: 18 (born October 24, 1990 in Lagos, Nigeria)...Son of Emeka Okafor Sr. and Patience Okafor...Has two brothers, Nonso (21) and T.J. (15), and two sisters, Chinealo (19) and Ral (10)...Third cousin of Charlotte Bobcats forward Emeka Okafor, who played collegiately at Connecticut and was No. 2 overall pick in the 2004 NBA draft...Other interests include reading, weightlifting and video games...Planning to major in biology/pre-med.
